data.description: This is the home you’ve been looking for! Beautifully updated 3 bedroom Row Home in the highly desirable Chalfont neighborhood of Far Northeast Philadelphia is ready for you to move right in. Lovingly cared for with modern upgrades throughout. Step inside the light filled and spacious living room with original hardwood floors. A unique, decorative tray ceiling was recently installed in the dining room and it is a show stopper! Enjoy the convenience of walking out to a deck right off of your dining room overlooking a fully fenced in backyard with a newer shed (2021). Modern updates to the kitchen include wood cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. An updated powder room on the main level has been newly fitted with a modern white vanity and upgraded faucet. Don’t miss the charming freshly painted wainscotting. Upstairs you will find 3 spacious bedrooms with ample closet space. The primary bedroom has 2 closets (including one walk in with shelving). A fully finished basement with tile that mimics wood flooring and exposed brick has potential to be sectioned off for a 4th bedroom or office with a front walkout and window. This middle of the row has a private driveway that is not shared. A brand new HVAC unit and hot water heater were just installed in 2023. Northeast Philadelphia is known for its accessibility to parks, shopping centers, schools and public transportation as well as quick access to main highways such as 95 and Route 1. This home is walkable to many local attractions. It is commuter friendly as Cornwell Heights train station is closeby, putting you in Center City Philadelphia in no time. Don’t miss this opportunity to own a modern, beautifully decorated and well maintained row home in Northeast Philadelphia!
